We’re all set. Your ticket (#{{ticket.id}}) has been resolved. Hopefully, you’re happy with the outcome. If not, simply reply to this email or click the link below to let Angus know. Remember - {{ticket.assignee.first_name}} is here to help.

https://support.itsolver.net/hc/en-au/requests/{{ticket.id}}

Thanks,
Your friend at IT Solver

